130    public GenericCustomObject<TValue> build() {
131        Objects.requireNonNull(id, CustomObject.class + ": id is missing");
132        Objects.requireNonNull(version, CustomObject.class + ": version is missing");
133        Objects.requireNonNull(createdAt, CustomObject.class + ": createdAt is missing");
134        Objects.requireNonNull(lastModifiedAt, CustomObject.class + ": lastModifiedAt is missing");
135        Objects.requireNonNull(container, CustomObject.class + ": container is missing");
136        Objects.requireNonNull(key, CustomObject.class + ": key is missing");
137        Objects.requireNonNull(value, CustomObject.class + ": value is missing");
138        return new GenericCustomObjectImpl<>(id, version, createdAt, lastModifiedAt, lastModifiedBy, createdBy,
139            container, key, value);
140    }
141
142    /**
143     * builds CustomObject without checking for non null required values
144     */
145    public GenericCustomObject<TValue> buildUnchecked() {
146        return new GenericCustomObjectImpl<>(id, version, createdAt, lastModifiedAt, lastModifiedBy, createdBy,
147            container, key, value);
148    }

150    public static <T> GenericCustomObjectBuilder<T> of(T value) {

154    }

156    public static <T> GenericCustomObjectBuilder<T> of(final GenericCustomObject<T> template) {
157        GenericCustomObjectBuilder<T> builder = new GenericCustomObjectBuilder<>();
158        builder.id = template.getId();
159        builder.version = template.getVersion();
160        builder.createdAt = template.getCreatedAt();
161        builder.lastModifiedAt = template.getLastModifiedAt();
162        builder.lastModifiedBy = template.getLastModifiedBy();
163        builder.createdBy = template.getCreatedBy();
164        builder.container = template.getContainer();
165        builder.key = template.getKey();
166        builder.value = template.getValue();
167        return builder;
168    }
